As the energon wave neared the mysterious bot, he did not move, that is not 
until the beam was just a few inches from him, that is when he simply side 
stepped, letting the beam fly past. him. He then boosted forward at an 
incredible speed as it drew two large double bladed sword type things and 
brought them infront of him the ends connecting together. He then slashed at 
Transmutate with both sides of the double sides double bladed staff/sword 
thing which glowed slightly with the deadly chaochitan energy that Hellpeon 
was so fond of using.

--part1_16c.3515413.2914707a_boundary
